metadata.name: Road of autumn leaves
metadata.description:
This is my first NFT photo work.

Japan has four seasons, and autumn is a very beautiful season with the changing leaves.
In the short time of autumn, I photographed a path of autumn leaves that can only be seen for a short time.
The trees stretching into the sky and the autumn leaves on the ground were beautiful and spectacular.

Photo data
Date taken: Nov. 25, 2021
Size: 4024x6048
